graph TD
    %% External Entities
    Student[Student]
    Staff[Staff]
    Admin[Admin]

    %% Processes
    P1(Authentication System)
    P2(Appointment Management)
    P3(Inventory Management)
    P4(Profile & User Management)
    P5(Notification System)

    %% Data Stores
    D1[(Users Database)]
    D2[(Appointments & History)]
    D3[(Inventory & Medicines)]
    D4[(Notifications)]

    %% Authentication Data Flows
    Student -->|Login/Signup Credentials| P1
    Staff -->|Login/Signup Credentials| P1
    Admin -->|Login Credentials| P1
    P1 <-->|Validate User & Check Role| D1
    P1 -->|Auth Token/Access| Student
    P1 -->|Auth Token/Access| Staff
    P1 -->|Auth Token/Access| Admin

    %% Appointment System Data Flows
    Student -->|Request Slot/Book| P2
    Staff -->|Request Slot/Book| P2
    P2 <-->|Check Availability/Create Appt| D2
    P2 -->|Booking Confirmation| Student
    P2 -->|Booking Confirmation| Staff
    P2 -->|View Medical History| Student
    P2 -->|View Medical History| Staff
    D2 <-->|Fetch Prescriptions| P2

    %% Inventory System Data Flows
    Admin -->|Add/Update/Scan Items| P3
    P3 <-->|Update Stock Levels| D3
    D2 -.->|Prescription Details| P3
    P3 -.->|Deduct Medicine Stock| D3

    %% Profile System Data Flows
    Student -->|Update Height/Weight| P4
    Staff -->|Update Profile Info| P4
    Admin -->|Manage User Accounts| P4
    P4 <-->|Update User Records| D1

    %% Notification System Data Flows
    P5 <-->|Fetch Alerts| D4
    P5 -->|Display Notifications| Student
    P5 -->|Display Notifications| Staff
    D1 -.->|User Group Info| P5
